---
layout: base.njk
title: "Browse Tags | #BuiltWithSerpApi"
---

<section class="browse-hero">
  <div class="shell">
    <h1>Browse by tag</h1>
    <p>Follow the use cases, product patterns, and builder categories emerging around SerpApi.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="shell browse-grid">
  {% for tag in tags %}
    <a class="browse-card" href="{{ ('/tags/' + (tag | slug) + '/') | url }}">
      <span class="mini-icon">{% icon "tag" %}</span>
      <span>{{ tag }}</span>
      <strong>{{ projects | relatedProjectCount(tag, "tags") }} project{% if projects | relatedProjectCount(tag, "tags") != 1 %}s{% endif %}</strong>
    </a>
  {% endfor %}
</section>
